# Cruise Problem

Sbt version: "1.10.0"
Scala version: "2.13.13"


## Code Structure

project/
│
├── build.sbt
│
├── README
│
├── src/
│   ├── main/
│   │   └── scala/
│   │       └── com/
│   │           └── tst/service
│   │               ├── PriceService.scala
│   │               └── PromotionService.scala
│   │
│   └── test/
│       └── scala/
│           └── com/
│               └── tst/service
│                   ├── PriceServiceSpec.scala
│                   └── PromotionServiceSpec.scala
│
└── project/
    └── build.properties



## Test
you can run test units in the following ways:

run ``` sbt test ```

or if you are using IntellJ IDEA you can go to each `*Spec` file and run each test file


